OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly
OL,6,Fsunny evening ahead. Then remaining
OL,7,Fdry with long clear spells overnight.
OL,8,FSome patchy low cloud developing in
OL,9,Fthe east later on. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FAny early low cloud in the
OL,12,Feast will quickly clear. Otherwise, a
OL,13,Fdry day with plenty of sunshine and
OL,14,Ffeeling very warm again.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA dry
OL,17,Ffew days with good spells of sunshine
OL,18,Fand remaining very warm or hot.
